8
00:02:34,362 --> 00:02:36,906
{\an8}- What's going on here?
- Dad?

9
00:02:39,576 --> 00:02:41,327
{\an8}I'm sorry, I just got startled.

10
00:02:43,997 --> 00:02:45,206
{\an8}Startled?

11
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:48,293
{\an8}That's how you react?

12
00:02:50,378 --> 00:02:54,465
- I thought someone broke in to rob us.
- You almost hit me.

13
00:02:54,549 --> 00:02:57,176
Well, why were you walking in the dark?

14
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:58,887
You should've turned on the lights!

15
00:02:58,970 --> 00:03:01,389
I just wanted to get some water.
I didn't want to wake anyone.

16
00:03:05,894 --> 00:03:09,480
Dear… No one can break in here to steal.

17
00:03:10,189 --> 00:03:11,316
I've got it covered.

18
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:15,403
I'm really sorry again.

19
00:03:18,364 --> 00:03:20,408
Okay. Take a rest now, Chiara.

20
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:12,437
Why aren't you sleeping yet?
Do you want some tea?

21
00:05:13,062 --> 00:05:15,106
Are you even able to sleep?

22
00:05:15,189 --> 00:05:18,276
