26
00:05:30,038 --> 00:05:31,581
It's about Chiara.

27
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:34,542
What's wrong with Chiara?

28
00:05:36,502 --> 00:05:38,504
Well, I don't know, love!

29
00:05:38,588 --> 00:05:40,548
