36
00:06:01,152 --> 00:06:02,779
So what's the problem?

37
00:06:03,362 --> 00:06:06,616
Of course, I'm worried about Mikoy.

38
00:06:06,699 --> 00:06:09,285
He's gotten himself into a dangerous life!

39
00:06:09,368 --> 00:06:10,536
Tess.

40
00:06:12,747 --> 00:06:14,123
