41
00:06:14,916 --> 00:06:16,876
This is Mikoy's life now.

42
00:06:17,919 --> 00:06:23,216
I just wish we had
better protection for our family.

43
00:06:23,299 --> 00:06:26,094
If we knew the truth.

44
00:06:28,513 --> 00:06:31,474
So keep getting close to Chiara.

45
00:06:35,645 --> 00:06:37,772
