46
00:06:56,207 --> 00:06:57,917
La Fornarina.

47
00:07:01,462 --> 00:07:04,590
{\an8}One of the famous paintings by Raphael.

48
00:07:04,674 --> 00:07:09,220
But you know,
Raphael isn't just a Ninja Turtle.

49
00:07:09,303 --> 00:07:11,389
He's also considered

50
00:07:11,472 --> 00:07:14,016
