Bad weeds take a long time to die.

80
00:12:54,523 --> 00:12:58,068
That's why as long as you live, do good.

81
00:12:58,152 --> 00:13:00,613
So I can atone for my sins in life.

82
00:13:00,696 --> 00:13:04,408
Oh, by the way,
how is my grandchild? Sofie.

83
00:13:06,118 --> 00:13:07,912
Oh my! She's growing up to be a weirdo.

84
