89
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:31,310
You're a good man
and a decent public servant.

90
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:34,813
Oh my! Thank you, Senator.

91
00:13:35,397 --> 00:13:37,399
By the way, what brings you here?

92
00:13:37,483 --> 00:13:38,984
