You can't just lie in bed all day.

115
00:15:37,102 --> 00:15:38,312
- True!
- This is important.

116
00:15:38,395 --> 00:15:41,649
- Yes.
- At least get some…

117
00:15:41,732 --> 00:15:44,485
- Let the blood flow.
- Blood flow. Let the blood flow.

118
00:15:44,568 --> 00:15:45,778
- Let the blood flow.
- Yes, flow.

119
00:15:45,861 --> 00:15:47,863
- Flow, so you'll recover.
- So you'll recover. Ready?

120
00:15:47,947 --> 00:15:49,448
- Okay, let's do this, child.
- Ready. Ready. Here we go.

121
00:15:49,531 --> 00:15:51,408
- We can do this. Come on!
- Okay.

122
