188
00:19:49,563 --> 00:19:53,901
on unified policing,
intelligence exchange,

189
00:19:53,984 --> 00:19:56,778
counter-terrorism,
organized crime suppression,

190
00:19:56,862 --> 00:19:59,823
and administrative synergy,

191
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:08,290
And because of that,

192
00:20:08,874 --> 00:20:12,961
it will be easier to build
our case against the Valtrovis

193
00:20:13,045 --> 00:20:15,797
and their Moraviano syndicate.

194
00:20:15,881 --> 00:20:19,384
When will this intelligence sharing…

195
00:20:22,095 --> 00:20:23,138
