an intelligence coordinator.

198
00:20:31,396 --> 00:20:34,441
And look, he's already here!

199
00:20:43,116 --> 00:20:44,910
What happened to you?

200
00:20:59,049 --> 00:21:01,176
Oh, Chiara. How are your parents?

201
00:21:01,260 --> 00:21:03,512
- Has your mother returned?
- Yes.

202
00:21:05,389 --> 00:21:09,309
And we just had a good breakfast earlier.

203
00:21:09,393 --> 00:21:10,727
How's your mom? How is she?

204
00:21:11,311 --> 00:21:12,771
She's doing okay.

205
00:21:15,774 --> 00:21:17,442
Still full of punchlines.

206
00:21:18,610 --> 00:21:24,324
She even told me she's the undisputed
beauty queen of Mabalacat.

207
00:21:24,408 --> 00:21:28,662
But when I met her, she seemed more like

208
00:21:28,745 --> 00:21:31,707
