- You're right!

210
00:21:34,501 --> 00:21:38,338
Actually, we were talking
about you earlier, Mikoy.

211
00:21:39,047 --> 00:21:43,010
Dad suggested that once you've recovered,

212
00:21:43,093 --> 00:21:45,595
