253
00:24:08,989 --> 00:24:11,449
Do you remember what I told you before,

254
00:24:11,533 --> 00:24:14,786
that rumor about the Valtrovi?

255
00:24:15,412 --> 00:24:17,038
The one spreading online?

256
00:24:18,206 --> 00:24:20,041
I have a friend, Dad.

257
00:24:20,125 --> 00:24:23,170
She said the rumor is actually true.

258
00:24:23,253 --> 00:24:26,089
That the Valtrovi are part of a syndicate.

259
00:24:26,923 --> 00:24:28,884
That's what her father said.

260
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:31,678
Who's her father?

261
00:24:33,972 --> 00:24:38,226
Not the president,
but a very reliable source.

262
00:24:38,894 --> 00:24:43,356
Her father is the director
of a major police agency,

263
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:46,276
the Government Agency
for Global Operations.

264
00:24:47,736 --> 00:24:50,238
Her father is the director there.

265
00:24:50,739 --> 00:24:53,408
General Norberto Ruiz.

266
00:25:02,667 --> 00:25:03,543
Is it true?

267
00:25:03,627 --> 00:25:06,087
That the government is going
to dissolve the agency?

268
00:25:16,264 --> 00:25:18,683
<i>The Valtrovis are part of a syndicate.</i>

269
00:25:18,767 --> 00:25:20,769
<i>Her father said that.</i>

270
00:25:21,269 --> 00:25:24,189
<i>He's General Norberto Ruiz.</i>

271
00:25:28,485 --> 00:25:29,736
Yes, this is Mikoy!

272
00:25:29,819 --> 00:25:31,529
You won't say, "How are you?"

273
00:25:31,613 --> 00:25:33,573
<i>I know that you miss me so much.</i>

274
00:25:35,784 --> 00:25:38,453
<i>What if Mikoy has a flaw?</i>

275
00:25:38,536 --> 00:25:41,539
<i>What if he's a womanizer?</i>

276
00:25:41,623 --> 00:25:43,458
But I'm trying to tell you that

277
00:25:43,541 --> 00:25:46,962
<i>Mr. Pinagpala is currently</i>
<i>on an indefinite leave.</i>

